Q: Wouldn&#8217;t purifying the senses make more experience?
<br>A: Experiencing what?
<br>Q: Experiencing through the senses more clearly.
<br>A: Its result is dispassion and not attachment.
<br>Q: Purifying the senses leads to more pleasurable experience through them.
<br>A: It is the pleasure of reality and not the senses. <span class=date>7/3/80</span>
